.html", "450f888f-98dd-57ca-6a07-317ae5cb77ae"], "hbd894a3dge179g4e16ga08cgf12559fb750b": ["I'll toast to that.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "39d77b7f-5370-93af-0d29-2d91fe85201c"], "h16f10631g4e2dg44abg9ce8g710004df5c9b": ["The pragmatic in me, however, sees only the silence before the storm.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "7d3bcd6a-9fb3-c4e8-7eab-1e054e32140b"], "he101cb8egaca4g42b0gb068gb82b017f365f": ["Something to sleep on. We should get some rest.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "bdce6e03-0ac7-bfe5-df18-4accffc7d86b"], "h3d8cdcd2gf80cg4670gbecfg84e8ccf7d855": ["Can you explain why the symptoms aren't showing?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "906961c6-57a4-f2ea-961c-4c697551dad2"], "h6206ccaeg202dg448cga804g33fe3ced8858": ["That, alas, is where my knowledge fails me.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "df523706-53bb-75be-73f0-cc2986baff9f"], "h9daa7245gfe45g4b1fga1ddg4f3e755ed835": ["A rogue might call it luck; a priest might call it fate.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "12dc0ce6-59cb-0cfd-6be0-6e4d35532f28"], "hd38219c5g20dfg49ecgb1e2gcc9204b087f6": ["As for myself: I'm a pragmatic. I see the silence before the storm.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "6a92085a-b1c6-a46a-17d4-7f750a4b7ed6"], "h0c50820dg1cd6g4d20g8fe0gbee636d63e81": ["And what makes you the expert?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "554c