, nothing at all.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "b5bc7ac8-9211-491e-de51-6c7bd4218853"], "ha1274dd0gf053g4d2aga15fgf3abbd9f0da7": ["Ah, yes. The good old days.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "a6ba4b3b-aa76-fc3e-5aad-b9a3bec1f736"], "h1e8f222cg7543g42e1g97d2g662de503e0f8": ["If you're about to start a lecture, I'm not interested.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "22b0b22f-c2fb-b368-5895-1d2f14f1829c"], "hb278a5b2gc855g414ag9a90g07c057ed3b7d": ["Long story short then:", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "c469bbcc-7822-002e-9ccb-465b58cec2a5"], "h43e452degaf7dg463fg847eg22f6faf62452": ["Thanks to the tadpole, we should have developed more than invasive symptoms by now, but we haven't.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "683281e6-db53-50d1-e831-b505cbbefad5"], "h45f55599g4d3bg42e4gb505ge7ab330a272f": ["A Githyanki's worst fate.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "011ee3f8-dd96-e7b9-73b7-1baf616ce362"], "h009a5ea9g6133g48b1g803dg23f15f5a58e0": ["Not the prettiest of transmutations, is it?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "ae67303c-1478-7421-304e-9caa6cad953f"], "hec41a287gf6ccg4a03ga2e2g1d233d3fc4f2": ["I saw Lae'zel giving you a look-over. Great minds think alike.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Gale.html", "7849d144-030b-3f7f-8e10-089b507c7d47"], "he2bf5e1agfa98g4992gbcd7g7372f034f2e4": ["No doubt she came to the same conclusion: 